          Health Insurance in Lausanne
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl text-gray-500 lg:mx-auto">
          Navigate Lausanne's healthcare system with mandatory LAMal/KVG insurance and optional supplementary coverage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <div class="prose prose-lg mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p>
